<plot>Gisela, an imaginative young girl who often reads fairy tails, is the unfortunate victim of her mother's abuse. Her only escape from her mother is to lock herself in her room and create a fantasy land inside her closet. This heart-wrenching dramatization is an attempt to bring a greater awareness to the thousands of kids across America who are victims of abuse or neglect.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?216279</url></doc>
